title: Dell Southeast Partner of the Year
text:
Dell Southeast Partner of the Year
Mavenspire, a leader in data center solutions, has been named Dell Southeast Region Partner of the Year at the DellWorld PartnerDirect Summit in Austin, Texas.
Annapolis, MD, October 22, 2015 --( PR.com )-- Mavenspire, a leader in data center solutions, has been named Dell Southeast Region Partner of the Year at the DellWorld PartnerDirect Summit in Austin, Texas. Each year honorees are selected based on their dedication to providing custom solutions for their clients using Dell technologies.
Mavenspire CEO, Michael Tanenhaus, technology veteran and thought leader, was present to accept this award and shared, “Winning this award could not have been possible without the support of all of our extended team members inside Dell who go the extra mile to ensure positive results for our clients.”
The annual awards that honor Dell partners for delivering exemplary solutions for their customers were presented at the Channel Partner Summit that kicked off Dell World 2015. These award winners are selected from a group of nominations based on their dedicated use of Dell technologies.
Mavenspire was pleased to accept the Dell Southeast Partner of the Year award. "Winning this award from Dell is a validation for our team of the things we do daily that put our mutual clients first. I am humbled to be selected,” remarked Tanenhaus.
Through a combination of sales growth, marketing and lead generation activities, technical training, and proactively promoting, Mavenspire has delivered outstanding results for Dell. The company looks forward to continuing the relationship in the coming year.
About Dell Enterprise Solutions: The Dell Enterprise Solutions portfolio provides complete end to end solutions for your datacenter including servers, storage, networking, data security, enterprise software, converged infrastructure, data management, analytics, and more.
About Mavenspire: Mavenspire’s experienced team provides data center solutions to large enterprises and mid-sized businesses all over the world. Our proven process combines expert assessment, architecture, design and implementation with the best-in-class data center solutions available today. We work with you to understand your goals, solve the tough problems and create a plan for your desired outcomes. Our goal is to be your partner every step of the way and inspire the future of your business. Learn more at http://www.mavenspire.com/ .
